videos.description: Texas' Jarrett Allen draws the foul and slams it home with the right hand against Baylor.
videos.headline: Texas' Allen throws down one-handed dunk

videos.description: Jarrett Allen rejects the two-handed dunk attempt as Texas looks to keep it close against No. 11 Baylor.
videos.headline: Texas' Allen swats dunk attempt with an anti-posterizer

videos.description: Baylor's Johnathan Motley collects the offensive rebound and makes the and-1 layup on the putback against Texas.
videos.headline: Baylor's Motley scores on second chance

videos.description: Baylor's Johnathan Motley takes the long pass from Jake Lindsey and makes the layup after drawing the foul to extend their lead over Texas.
videos.headline: Great look sets up another and-1 for Motley

videos.description: Jo Lual-Acuil drives to the basket and makes the off-balance shot to help extend Baylor's lead over Texas.
videos.headline: Baylor's Lual-Acuil Jr. beats the shot clock

videos.description: Baylor's Nuni Omot catches the lob from Jake Lindsey and throws down the two handed dunk as Baylor tries to pull away from Texas.
videos.headline: Baylor executes inbound play perfectly for monster dunk

videos.description: Johnathan Motley talks about what Baylor needs to do to be successful in the postseason.
videos.headline: Johnathan Motley on what's next for Baylor

videos.description: Fran Fraschilla explains why Baylor has what it takes to go deep into the postseason.
videos.headline: ESPN's Fran Fraschilla talks about Baylor's potential
